              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "169Tm target foil of thickness ~0.5 mg/cm2 was prepared",
                "by rolling technique.",
                "The Al-catcher foils (20 to 50 ug/cm2 thick) was",
                "prepared using thermal evaporation vacuum deposition",
                "technique."
              ]
            }
          ],
